data.description: **The current loan is assumable and has a 2.25% interest rate**  Looking for a warm home that is nestled within minutes to wineries, shopping, and exploration? Look no further! Located in the immaculately manicured Crowne Hill neighborhood, step into the tranquility and relaxation of a wonderfully bright an open home that is made for those who like to gather and entertain!  Built to cater to everyone, this beautiful 5 bedroom home boasts a full on-suite downstairs bedroom which has been quipped with handicapped bars to accommodate special living, an enclosed office, and a large open den that can be used as a downstairs office, dining room, or more!   The expansive kitchen offers a large island and is perfect for dinner parties and family gatherings, while the cozy family room is equipped with a fireplace to keep you and your guests warm. As you step out into the breathtaking back yard, you are met with a pristine pool with a gargling waterfall that creates a bubble of peace and relaxation.  The stairs opens onto the second level into an extensive open loft that allows for more space to create the house of your dreams!  The spacious primary bedroom flows into a bathroom with a soaking tub, shower, dual sinks, and a dual walk in closet with two separate entry doors that will make you the envy of your friends!  Lastly, but not least, the downstairs laundry room comes with the washer and dryer, and the doorway to the garage opens into a large space that extends into the two car parking spaces. This front and back spacing is unique and provides you with the opportunity for a home gym, or extra room for storage.  To add a cherry on top, this home has solar, keeping your energy bill low on those hot summer days!  Come and see this beautiful home for yourself, as the pictures cannot tell you the endless possibilities that it holds in store for you!!
